2x_2 = 2x_1
x_1=x_2
(x_1 + 1)(x_2 - 1) = (x_2 + 1)(x_1 - 1)
2x_2 = 2x_1
x_1 = x_2
\dfrac{x+1}{x-1}
1 + \dfrac{2}{x-1}
 1 + \frac{2}{x_1-1}= 1 + \frac{2}{x_2-1}
 \implies  \frac{2}{x_1-1}=\frac{2}{x_2-1} 
\implies \frac{x_1-1}{2}=\frac{x_2-1}{2}
\implies x_1-1=x_2-1 
\implies x_1=x_2
